<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >How powerful is data activism?</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resImageText section">


























		<div class="row" id="15a64e5f-c5ac-435c-a139-ad3f28be50fb">
